{"_path":"/tags/tools/github","_dir":"tools","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"Github","description":"GitHub 是一个功能强大的代码托管平台，为开发者提供了丰富的工具和功能，帮助他们更高效地进行代码管理、协作和部署。GitHub的广泛应用和活跃的开发者社区使其成为全球最受欢迎的代码托管平台之一","name":"github","icon":"carbon:logo-github","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"github"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"GitHub"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"icon","props":{"className":["size-32"],"name":"logos:github"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"GitHub 是一个基于 Git 版本控制系统的代码托管平台，旨在帮助开发者协作、管理和分享代码。以下是 GitHub 的一些关键特点："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"版本控制"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：GitHub 提供了强大的 Git 版本控制功能，使开发者能够跟踪代码的变化、协作开发和管理代码历史。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"代码托管"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：开发者可以在 GitHub 上创建仓库（Repository）来存储和管理代码，方便团队协作和代码共享。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"协作工具"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：GitHub 提供了 Issues、Pull Requests、Projects 等协作工具，方便团队成员进行讨论、代码审查和项目管理。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"部署服务"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：GitHub Pages 服务允许开发者将静态网站部署到 GitHub 上，提供免费的托管服务。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"社交网络"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：GitHub 是一个开发者社交平台，开发者可以关注其他开发者、Star 项目、Fork 项目等，促进开发者之间的交流和学习。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"持续集成"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：GitHub Actions 提供了持续集成和部署功能，开发者可以通过配置 Workflows 来自动化构建、测试和部署流程。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"安全性"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：GitHub 提供了代码扫描、漏洞警报等安全功能，帮助开发者保障代码安全。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"总的来说，GitHub 是一个功能强大的代码托管平台，为开发者提供了丰富的工具和功能，帮助他们更高效地进行代码管理、协作和部署。GitHub 的广泛应用和活跃的开发者社区使其成为全球最受欢迎的代码托管平台之一。"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":5,"depth":5,"links":[{"id":"github","depth":2,"text":"GitHub"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:tags:tools:github.md","_source":"content","_file":"tags/tools/github.md","_extension":"md"}